The paper deals with solving influence diagrams, which are a type of probabilistic graphical model used in decision making under uncertainty. This falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of branch-and-bound search involves exploring a search tree, which is a common technique in algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the practical implementation of the algorithm, which could fall under the category of robotics and control systems (cs.SY) or multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
